data.Name: VINCINT
data.Bio: Vincint Cannady (born April 5, 1991), known by the mononym Vincint (stylized as VINCINT), is an American singer and songwriter. He is best known as a finalist on the first season of the singing competition The Four. He released his debut EP, The Feeling on February 14, 2020. Cannady later released his debut studio album, There Will Be Tears on June 11, 2021. Vincint Cannady was born and raised in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania.
